                "IOCH",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Three delta E-E spectrometers, two of",
                "which had a delta E detector of a three-channel",
                "ionization chamber, the third has a silicon detector",
                "40 um thick. Flowing argon was used as the working",
                "gas in the ionization chamber. The energy loss of the",
                "ions in the ionization chamber corresponded to that",
                "deposited in an approximately 15 um thick silicon",
                "detector. Silicon with 1 mm thickness was used as E",
                "detectors in all spectrometers."
              ]
            }
